  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Urgent Covid Relief for Girls to Continue Learning</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Edu-GIRLS&apos; agenda to lift girls out of poverty using its 10 Mantra approach had been jolted by COVID threatening financial ruin, leaving girls on the street and arresting learning. A $100,000  COVID Action Agenda I has distributed 1M meals, set up 600 digital learning devices and motivated  teachers to worker smarter. With COVID wave 2, the fight intensifies. Vaccination drives and basic treatment facilities need to be set up to save girls, families and staff and prepare for school reopening.</narrative>
  </description>
